flowRoot.flowPara: 1. Place the Evo inside the starting circle
2. Surround the Evo with your hands
3. The Evo will spin as long as it is surrounded by your hands. The longer it spins, the further it will go when you move your hands - but if you wait too long you will lose your turn!
4. Move your hands to send the Evo as straight as possible down the course
